invalid type: string "Non-core pattern:\nPioneer\nGaetano, you differ in most ways from the\nPioneer pattern, but you share some\ncharacteristics with Pioneers in that you are\ncontextual, someone who appreciates\ncolleagues with diverse skillsets, and\nexploratory.\nHOW TO ENGAGE THEM\nBe lively and open to exploring ideas\nHear them out; they often think out loud\nBrainstorm using visuals\n’’’’’